I shopped @qvc ‘scurated Mother’s Day gift guides to put together this FUN gift basket for mom.🎁
We LOVE giving baskets because you can fill it with all your mom’s favorite things to show her how much you appreciate her.
I chose:
🤍 The Marigold Garden Tool Set - Because my mom LOVES to garden
🤍 The Giving Heart Pillow - to remind her how much she’s loved
🤍The 6-piece Skincare Set - To keep her skin glowy during our travels
🤍The Whipped Argan Body Butter - to keep her skin moisturized and hydrated
🤍The XO Aromatherapy Dough - to help ease stress
